quickstart:
Install with `npm install --save-dev @gravity-ui/axios-wrapper`. Subclass AxiosWrapper to create your API client:

```javascript
import AxiosWrapper from '@gravity-ui/axios-wrapper';

export class API extends AxiosWrapper {
    getProjects() {
        return this.get('/projects');
    }
}

const apiInstance = new API({
    config: { baseURL: '/api/v2' },
    collector: { collectErrors: 10, collectRequests: 10 }
});
```

Supports automatic cancellation of concurrent requests via `concurrentId` option, CSRF token injection via `setCSRFToken()`, custom default headers via `setDefaultHeader()`, and request collection/logging via the `collector` option.
